    {
      "ruleId": "hz.web.7079c4792fd903c2.rule.2",
      "text": "Your use must also be consistent with applicable law and align with LinkedIn’s values (which include, but are not limited to, not using the Brand in a misleading, unfair, defamatory, infringing, libelous, disparaging, obscene, or otherwise objectionable manner).",
